Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的一颗便是宽600公里的谷神星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The largest asteroid is 600-mile-wide Ceres,
