Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇求鲁布陨石撞击的一百倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the impactor that caused the Chicxulub impact,
