Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事实上要更加糟糕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it's a really, really bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是远糟于圣经故事中的灾难的浩劫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be a disaster far beyond biblical proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将会导致\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would create a crater
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个差不多和美国一样大的坑痕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}nearly as big as the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But while it was doing that,
