Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪入目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是  谷神星围绕着太阳运转稳定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Luckily, Ceres is in a stable orbit around the sun,
