Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从最近的信息看来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the smaller ones present a tougher challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型个体才是更大的挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as the latest information shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型行星的数量远多于大型行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's far more small ones than large ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  假若要列举\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, if you say the objects that are
