Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且已经发现其中的10%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we've discovered 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若看更小的小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if you move to smaller still objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30米左右的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}30 meter and larger-sized objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为大概有两百万个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we think there's about two million of those objects
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们已经发现的还不到1%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we've discovered much less than 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来十年会出现更好的望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Better telescopes coming online over the next decade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将为天文学家发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will allow astronomers to identify
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多的小行星提供可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}many more asteroids of all sizes.
