Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管尺寸不大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Something that size
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却仍可能是致命一击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could still pack a devastating punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上布满了过去小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The earth is covered with evidence of past collisions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞击的证据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with asteroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今科学家们废寝忘食的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And today's scientists are working feverishly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能预测出将来的发展\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to figure out what's coming next.
