Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经洗劫了地球的大部分生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}most life on the planet in the past.
