Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}布鲁斯·贝茨\N行星协会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百万甚至数千百万年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's measured in many millions
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会来袭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or tens of millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它们的大块头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they're big enough that through our observations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以让我们通过观察来定位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we know where those objects are.
