Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为其频率更高而且不易于发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as they happen more often and they're harder to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下其中一颗小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine that one of these smaller asteroids
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向城市俯冲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is streaking toward a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而直到迫在眉睫的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It may not be spotted
