Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及疏散人群\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}leaving little time for evacuation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:14:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更没有机会将它扼杀在宇宙中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and no chance to try and deflect it in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设撞击宽度为100英尺\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If it's about 100 feet wide on impact,
