Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.07,0:33:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着我们也许可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That means we might be able to deflect them
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.00,0:33:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它们撞上地球之前改变它们的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before they hit the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.00,0:33:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  一颗彗星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.36,0:33:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从太阳系中飞来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}comes in from the outer depths of the solar system,
