Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.90,0:33:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们很难得到警告\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, we have very little warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.35,0:33:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是  绝大部分有可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fortunately, most of the things that potentially
