Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.48,0:33:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们能非常精确地追踪它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And we can track the asteroids pretty accurately.
