Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2025年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By 2025,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望新型宇宙飞船能够长途旅行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we expect new spacecraft designed for long journeys
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.14,0:34:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我们可以送人上天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to allow us to begin the first ever crewed missions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.18,0:34:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入比月球还要遥远的外太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the moon into deep space.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.53,0:34:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们将史上首次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So we'll start by sending astronauts to an asteroid
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.53,0:34:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送宇航员登上小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the first time in history.
