Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.51,0:34:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻一代  他们想走得更远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the younger generations, they wanna go beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.34,0:34:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你知道我的祖父母上过月球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, my grandparents went to the moon, you know.
