Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓舞人心的部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the president's message,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.78,0:34:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国宇航局需要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we need to get NASA back
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.36,0:34:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新投身到外太空事业中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into the business of deep space.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.35,0:34:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载人飞船登上小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A manned mission to an asteroid will be very different
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.97,0:34:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟过去登上月球是大不相同的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from moon missions of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.18,0:34:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些方面更容易\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In some ways, it will be easier,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.51,0:34:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一些方面  要难得多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and in other ways, much harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.91,0:34:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论宇航员要去哪颗小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whichever asteroid the astronauts visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.38,0:34:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离比去月球都要远得多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will likely be a lot farther from earth than the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.98,0:35:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以行程可能持续几个月\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the journey will probably last for months,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.58,0:35:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而去月球只要八天时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}instead of the eight days it takes to get to the moon.
