Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.45,0:35:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在月球的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you go to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.37,0:35:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要对付身体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you're dealing with a body
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.82,0:35:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显的重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with significant gravity of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.02,0:35:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将不得不全程使用更多的燃料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're having to use more fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.56,0:35:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来减慢速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to safely slow yourself down
