Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你走了更远的路才到达那里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even though you're going farther to get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.01,0:35:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却不必为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you aren't having to expend
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似着陆之类的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}nearly as much fuel for things
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.28,0:35:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花费那么多的燃料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like getting to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.47,0:35:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你离开小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It also takes less propulsion ability
