Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.26,0:35:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要更少的推进力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to head back to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在小行星表面着陆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But landing on an asteroid's surface
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.21,0:35:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟登陆月球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be much more challenging
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.10,0:35:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比是更大的挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than setting down on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.22,0:35:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比登陆  它更像入港\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's more like docking than it is landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.39,0:35:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你还是有些重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but you do have some gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.12,0:35:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得对付这一点点重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you have to deal with having a little bit of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.40,0:36:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须让自己精确抛锚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But you have to deal with actually anchoring yourself,
