Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.72,0:36:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全脱离这颗行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and escape from the asteroid completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.60,0:36:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你探险的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you have to make sure that you're tethered down,
