Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.67,0:36:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送宇航员登上小行星呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to send astronauts to an asteroid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.39,0:36:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员  探险家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronauts, explorers,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公众都对太空很有兴趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the public interested in space
