Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.18,0:42:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照它行进的路线  本该撞上地球的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On its way in, it was going to collide with the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.05,0:42:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于大气压力的作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it skipped off of the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.18,0:42:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它掠过了大气层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}due to the pressure of the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.41,0:42:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像打水漂一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like a pebble being skipped off
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.19,0:42:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵石掠过湖面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the surface of a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.96,0:42:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是次亲密接触\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That was a really close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.16,0:42:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后的2008年10月\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then, in October 2008, a small and seemingly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.46,0:42:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在非洲苏丹的偏远地区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}uneventful impact occurred in a remote part
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.80,0:42:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一次看似无关痛痒的冲撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the African country of Sudan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.17,0:42:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可它象征了人类在预测小行星撞击领域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it actually represented a giant step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.17,0:42:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨出的一大步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the science of predicting asteroid impacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.18,0:42:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们发现了一颗小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A small asteroid was discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.44,0:42:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并预测它会在第二天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it was predicted to land
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.18,0:42:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在苏丹落地  最后的确如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in Sudan the next day, and it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.02,0:42:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们第一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, this is the first case we have of an object
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.56,0:42:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测到一个物体  并预测出它落地的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that was discovered and then predicted to land
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.16,0:42:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详尽时间与地点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at a particular time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.73,0:43:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  随后人们在沙漠中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in fact, fragments of this object were later found
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.10,0:43:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了它的碎片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}over the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.00,0:43:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that was only
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.99,0:43:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次只有一天预警的撞击不过是米粒之珠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a small impact with a single day's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.54,0:43:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今  我们到底有没有能力去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today, the jury is still out on whether we'll be able
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.74,0:43:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别并避免一次毁灭地球的灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to identify and deflect something that could inflict
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.58,0:43:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还尚无定论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}catastrophic damage on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.02,0:43:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家们相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists believe there are still millions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.22,0:43:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数未知的小行星仍飘荡在宇宙中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of unidentified asteroids out there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.19,0:43:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们可能摧毁一座城市\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}capable of destroying a city...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.34,0:43:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或更糟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.70,0:43:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能找出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will we be able to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.14,0:43:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不速之客吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which ones will cross our path?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.93,0:43:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能阻止它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And will we be able to prevent them from
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.94,0:43:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞上地球吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}slamming into earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.21,0:43:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们承受不起如此之高的风险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The stakes couldn't possibly be any higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.58,0:43:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小行星的每一点新发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each new discovery in the world of asteroids
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.80,0:43:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不仅仅象征着科技的进步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}isn't just a scientific advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.56,0:43:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更意味着人类幸存下去的概率有可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but an opportunity to increase the survival chances
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.56,0:44:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此提升\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of mankind.
